videos.description: Villanova's Jalen Brunson finds Omari Spellman down low for the emphatic dunk.
videos.headline: Spellman throws down loud dunk

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall finds Mikal Bridges open in the corner for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Paschall finds Bridges for corner 3-pointer

videos.description: Lafayette's Matt Klinewski grabs his missed shot attempt and goes up strong with the layup.
videos.headline: Klinewski converts second-chance bucket

videos.description: Lafayette's Matt Klinewski gets the ball in the post and is fouled on the layup attempt for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Klinewski converts 3-point play

videos.description: Villanova's Mikal Bridges swings the ball to Phil Booth in the corner for a contested 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Booth knocks down contested 3

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall drives to the lane and draws contact on the layup in the first half.
videos.headline: Paschall drives to the rack for a 3-point play

videos.description: Lafayette's Paulius Zalys breaks out in transition and slams the dunk down in the first half.
videos.headline: Zalys throws down emphatic dunk

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall swings the ball to Jalen Brunson at the top of the arch for a 3-pointer in the second half.
videos.headline: Wildcats' ball movement leads to open 3

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall takes the pass from Eric Stafford and drives to the rack for the tough layup.
videos.headline: Paschall drives to the lane for and-1 layup

videos.description: Jalen Brunson lobs a pass from downtown to Mikal Bridges for the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Wildcats extend lead on alley-oop

videos.description: Villanova's Jalen Brunson finds Phil Booth on the break for the layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Brunson finds Booth in transition for the layup

videos.description: Jermaine Samuels quickly inbounds the ball to Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree driving to the rack for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Villanova executes inbound play for 3-point chance
